channel.title: Help?
channel.description:
@echo off title InternationPK cd ./Class/ "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_03\bin\java.exe" -Xmx512m Gui 30 0 lowmem members 32
and it says
Error: could not find or load main class : Gui
if it is my classpath or path what should it be?

item.title: Help?
item.dc:creator: @Dremorain Dremorain
item.description:
@Dremorain wrote:

the command cd ./Class/ is looking for your Gui in that folder. if it’s in the same folder with the compiler, just remove that line. if it’s in a different folder, adjust accordingly. 202685 has the right idea.

Read full topic
